447
00:45:32,320 --> 00:45:33,360
[SPEAKER_01] Ne, ne možete.

448
00:45:34,000 --> 00:45:35,280
[SPEAKER_01] Pa, da, to je isto.

449
00:45:35,519 --> 00:45:40,320
